{
  "answer": "Mirza Ghalib's famous ghazal opens with the requested couplet (sher), from *Diwan-E-Ghalib*.[^1]\n\n**Original (Urdu):**\n\n> عشق مجھ کو نہیں وحشت ہی سہی  \n> میری وحشت تری شہرت ہی سہی[^2]\n\n**Transliteration:**\n\n> Ishq mujh ko nahin vehshat hi sahi  \n> Meri vehshat teri shohrat hi sahi[^3]\n\n**Translation:**\n\n> If not your love, this wild obsession—so be it;  \n> My obsession only builds your fame—then so be it.[^4]\n\nThis is the matla (opening couplet) of the full ghazal, which continues in the radif \"hi sahi\" (\"so be it\").[^5]\n\n[^1]: Mirza Ghalib, *Diwan-E-Ghalib*, ch. 84 [Ishq mujh ko nahin vehshat hi sahi](/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/84-ishq-mujh-ko-nahin-vehshat-hi-sahi/).\n\n[^2]: [/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/84-ishq-mujh-ko-nahin-vehshat-hi-sahi/original/#p-c00f68](works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/84-ishq-mujh-ko-nahin-vehshat-hi-sahi/original/#p-c00f68).\n\n[^3]: [/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/84-ishq-mujh-ko-nahin-vehshat-hi-sahi/transliteration/#p-086cb4](/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/84-ishq-mujh-ko-nahin-vehshat-hi-sahi/transliteration/#p-086cb4).\n\n[^4]: [/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/84-ishq-mujh-ko-nahin-vehshat-hi-sahi/translation/#p-a4c81f](/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/84-ishq-mujh-ko-nahin-vehshat-hi-sahi/translation/#p-a4c81f).\n\n[^5]: Mirza Ghalib, *Diwan-E-Ghalib*, ch. 84 [Ishq mujh ko nahin vehshat hi sahi](/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/84-ishq-mujh-ko-nahin-vehshat-hi-sahi/translation/).",
